text: Half-buried on the asteroid's surface you find a deserted Gzilt dreadnaught. Its cryo-arithmetic engines are leaking deuterium.
In the crater you salvage a wrecked Eagle-class shuttle. You board and find the crew have disappeared.
The scrap merchant sells you a laser carbine. When you pull the trigger, it takes you 8 minutes back in time.
In the waste dump you uncover a kinetic mortar. When you try to fire it, it annihilates itself.
On the derelict hypermatter tanker you uncover a rusty hyperdrive. When you try to switch it on, it refuses to do anything.
In the alien tomb you identify a mass-driver mortar. When you try to fire it, tiny cyber-bugs start swarming out of a hole in the side.
In the trash compactor you find a quantum blaster. When you pull the trigger, there's a blinding flash and it's... gone.
Drifting in space, a sensor ping shows a deserted Intrepid-class interceptor. When you board you find the crew have been... disassembled?
@Chris_S_Gosse You blast the mint-condition interceptor, just as the crew return from their lunch break. They are not best pleased.
